channel.name: Custom_merge spaces - HL7 > DB
channel.description:
This channel is an LLP listener that accepts incoming HL7 messages and then stores some of the information to a database. The Source component listens for messages on port 5145. The Destination component inserts some of the fields from the message into a SQLite database.
See http://help.interfaceware.com/v6/hl7-to-database
